==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Big reds and big purples

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà hóng dà zĭ

===Idiom===
'''[[大紅]][[大]][[紫]]''' 

# To become very popular.
# To be a prominent person.

#: ''[[這個]][[歌星]][[正]]'''大紅大紫'''[[著]][[呢]].''

